ies are needed for understanding the tensor structure\nof the spin-1 deuteron, including a new mechanism to explain the large\ndifferences between the current data and our theoretical results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2017 13:37:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Apr 2017 19:27:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 May 2017 09:50:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-24"}
